,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"曬命我屌你老母"},{"pid":"328462a2e1a8b6613c89836cc9c5545026e94684","tid":534993,"uid":69260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:25:34.000Z","msg":"Same here ar巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我同對方係未正式拍拖，不過都日見夜見，曖曖昧昧咁。<br />\n我同你一樣，都係想對方開心，<br />\n有樣野唔知係好事定壞事，我屋企附近有通宵小巴去佢住果度既附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 坐完車仲要行上山先番到屋企。。<br />\n話就話唔駛趕尾班車，幾夜都有車，但轉錢一程8蚊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家既心態都係反正有通宵車，幾夜都係8蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有幾次仲8蚊坐上去，送佢上去，5分鐘都冇，又8蚊坐番落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我習慣左次次同佢出街都送到佢去佢屋企果度，識左佢5個月，次次見都送。目前依然維持不敗紀錄。。<br />\n起初都話送到樓下就算，到而家送埋上走廊添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時候同佢去到咁夜，真係驚佢一個女仔咁夜有危險，唔放心。<br />\n<br />\n總結，重點係車錢好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋我日日要番9，7點要起身，已經幾個月冇訓超過5個鐘，就變喪屍就死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到群主個post，好有共鳴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98ed6020441f152fd77216a0a3f234d01b2f72d","tid":534993,"uid":135828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:31:07.000Z","msg":"一齊幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67957bb1a956bc0385cf14f15c44c72b7e7906f0","tid":534993,"uid":1740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fe8f84ee6bdc5c5197c7f6dfa0dd4e74ff50ffe","tid":534993,"uid":1740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:39:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb1013ddc702e3a0ad6b7a30de48b81b025c25ac","tid":534993,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,