ockquote><br />\n<br />\n調教下男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d12c240b1088d7b5337107039cd121a4dad376c","tid":534993,"uid":98333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T23:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又真係好煩嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e092cf2ac3582ccbf19a9c31cdcfe880661cfce5","tid":534993,"uid":98333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T23:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫佢搬黎你到住囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢訓得唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3ee7fa7cce033bf06a8a16ecb7dec9f08e156a","tid":534993,"uid":98333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T23:28:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話人身在福中不知福個啲我唔信你一世都無屌過老母太煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔關你事梗係sweet啦</span></span><br />\n到你女朋友24小時都痴住你個時你就唔會咁講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d4ec392d63296b74592f7acc3c74a4115f9811","tid":534993,"uid":98333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T23:29:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咪一路提住有咩做<br />\n今晚實沒得訓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢覺得佢可以陪住我做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7166c13c02394278df202a122cec8043d00c218d","tid":534993,"uid":98333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T23:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>娶左佢囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c71d226326a4b5919b5cea322acc27b7d26cc6","tid":534993,"uid":98333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0